app_name: 唱响音符 - 助力音乐梦想
developer: Beijing Shidai Note Network Technology Co., Ltd.
description:
大众参与，万众创新，边听·边玩·边赚，和有趣的人一起听歌、互动、看玩音乐，用音乐连接彼此，用音乐传递美好力量！

唱响音符APP是一款音乐数字版权收益共享平台。在这里有好玩好听的音乐，让你大饱耳福；在这里有音乐大咖/音乐爱好者，让你轻松结识拥有相同兴趣的朋友。
平台拥有完整的音乐创作、歌曲发行、推广变现、交易众筹等服务，致力于打造数字资产音乐文化服务平台，为音乐行业带来全新的发展机遇。主要面向音乐粉丝、爱好者、音乐人、音乐机构、版权方等群体，提供包括版权交易、打造爆款歌曲等多种服务，助力音乐行业实现更加多元化的创新发展，重新定义原创音乐版权价值，打造完整原创音乐共创共赢的模式。

在这里，粉丝们能获得与偶像共创音乐的回馈福利。在此等共赢生态下，建立一个优质、高效且安全可靠的原创音乐社交平台，赋能音乐创作者为华语乐坛带来更好的作品。推动音乐行业的良性发展，探索原创音乐世界的一切可能。如果你是音乐创作人，那就快来参与音乐创作的殿堂，如果你是音乐同好者，那就快来邂逅好音乐吧。

产品特色：
【抢先试听】精选优质艺人数字音乐，粉丝专属定制衍生品福利。为你喜欢的音乐打call，好音乐等你来发掘；
【全球发行】全球渠道免费上架，多维度多场景歌曲版税收益变现；
【安全可靠】创作时间轴，提供创作历史可信记录，不可篡改；
【词曲交易】优势资源互补，科技助力全球创作者、厂牌成功；
【百万征稿】实现创作梦想 ，为大咖明星创作词曲，与明星艺人共同创作，发挥你的音乐才华；
【整合营销】词曲邀约、艺人合作、制作、发行，优势资源互补，创作更有价值的音乐；
【收益多样】为音乐创作者提供多种收益模式，可买断、可按比例出让收益，持续获得分成；

有什么想吐槽的，请随时联系我们：
微信公众号：唱响音符

邮箱：tech@meta-boom.com.cn

What's that song? Shazam will instantly identify music playing around you or in apps like TikTok, Instagram, YouTube & Snapchat. Discover concerts near you, song lyrics, videos & more. With tens of millions of daily users, Shazam is trusted by music lovers worldwide.

“Shazam is a gift... a game changer” – Pharrell Williams, GQ 
“I don't know how we ever survived before Shazam” – Marshmello 
“Shazam is a kind of magic… You hear a song, hold your phone up like a wand and it tells you exactly what song it is, who sang it and lets you add it to your playlist or share it to your social media… How is that not magic?!” – Calum Scott

WHY YOU’LL LOVE IT

* Identify music in an instant.
* Discover live shows near you from your favourite artists or through curated recommendations.
* Recognise songs even when you’re offline, using headphones or on a different app.
* Revisit your music discovery history in your library anytime.
* Get recommended songs and playlists similar to the music you’ve discovered.

USE SHAZAM ANYWHERE, ANYTIME

* Enable the Shazam widgets on your Lock Screen or Home Screen.
* Ask Siri, “What’s this song?” to use Shazam hands-free.
* Automate music discovery with the Shazam Shortcut in the Shortcuts app.

CONNECT WITH YOUR MUSIC

* Unlock extras from artists around the world.
* Open any song directly in Apple Music, Spotify, YouTube Music, Amazon Music & Deezer.
* Listen and add songs directly to your Apple Music playlists.
* Watch music videos of the songs you discover in Apple Music or YouTube.
* Follow along to songs with real-time, karaoke-style lyrics.
* See what’s trending locally and globally with Shazam Charts.

Availability and features may vary by country. For more information on Shazam’s privacy practices, please read the Privacy Policy, available at https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/. Find out more and get support from AppleCare at https://support.apple.com/guide/shazam/welcome.

Welcome to djay! The #1 DJ app and winner of multiple Apple Design Awards now integrates with Apple Music - mix over 100 million songs instantly!

djay transforms your iOS device into a full-featured DJ system. Seamlessly integrated with your music library, djay allows you to mix your favorite songs and playlists. You can perform live, remix tracks, or enable Automix mode to let djay create a seamless mix for you automatically. Whether you are a professional DJ or a beginner who just loves to play with music, djay offers you the most intuitive yet powerful DJ experience on an iOS device. 

APPLE MUSIC INTEGRATION

• Access to over 100 million songs
• Match: recommendations based on the currently playing song 
• Your library: all your music seamlessly integrated
• Listen Now and Charts integration 
• Discover new music and add songs to your Apple Music library right from within djay
• Powerful search capabilities for the vast catalog of Apple Music

ADVANCED MEDIA LIBRARY

• Apple Music: 100+ million tracks, your personal library in the cloud (Apple Music subscription)
• TIDAL: Millions of tracks, high quality sound (TIDAL DJ Extension)
• SoundCloud: Millions of underground and premium tracks (SoundCloud Go+)
• Beatport: Millions of electronic music tracks (Beatport Advanced Subscriptions)
• Beatsource: Millions of open-format music tracks (Beatsource Subscription)
• Files: access files in the cloud (e.g. Dropbox), on your iOS device, or on external hard drives seamlessly
• My Collection: Powerful playlists management 

AUTOMIX

• Automatic, beat-matched mixes 
• Queue and Playlist automation

NEURAL MIX™

• Isolate vocals, drums, and instrumentals in real-time (not supported with Apple Music)

MUSIC PRODUCTION TOOLS

• Sequencer: create beats on top of your music live
• Looper: remix your music with up to 48 loops per track
• Beat-matched sequencing of drums and samples
• Extensive content library with hundreds of loops and samples.

HARDWARE INTEGRATION

• Plug-and-play integration with over 100 MIDI controllers by Pioneer DJ, Reloop, Hercules, Numark, Denon DJ, and more
• Digital Vinyl System (DVS) Integration
• Advanced MIDI Learn to map any class-compliant MIDI controller
• Support for Bluetooth audio and MIDI
• Support for multi-channel USB audio interfaces and video output

POWERFUL AUDIO ENGINE

• Ableton Link integration
• Fluid Beatgrid
• High-res waveforms

BUILT FOR iOS

• Accessible via VoiceOver
• Airplay, Live Photos, Apple Watch, and iCloud integration
• Haptic Feedback, Drag & Drop, Keyboard Shortcuts
• Multi-Tasking: Slide Over and Split View support

Top features of the optional Pro subscription include: 

• Unlimited access to an extensive library of samples, loops, FX, and visuals 
• Neural Mix™
• Sampler & Looper 
• Automix 
• Crossfader FX 
• Video Mixing 
• Music Visualizers
• Single Deck mode
• 4-Deck mode 
• Advanced media library editing
• Pre-cueing with headphones 
• Hardware integration (MIDI controllers, DVS, multi-channel audio interfaces)
• 7-day free trial: free access to all djay Pro content and features for one week, cancel anytime

The optional PRO subscription allows you to subscribe once and use djay Pro across all your Mac and iOS devices, including access to all PRO features, as well as 1000+ loops, samples, and visuals.

A supported streaming subscription and an internet connection are required to access songs from a streaming service in djay. No recording available for streamed songs. Neural Mix cannot be used when streaming from Apple Music. Specific songs may not be available or accessible on your account or in your country. Streaming service availability and pricing may vary depending on country, currency and service.

Midi DJ remote lite is a MIDI controller for PC/Mac DJ software, including Traktor Pro 2, Deckadance 2, Mixxx, Torq, and any other MIDI-enabled DJ software.

It allows you to send and receive MIDI messages over a Wi-Fi network, enabling remote control of your PC/Mac DJ software. With Midi DJ remote lite, you can eliminate the need for a mouse and trackpad. This app is fully compatible with Traktor Pro 2 for both Mac and PC, and it consists of DeckA, DeckB, and Mixer functionalities.

**DeckA/DeckB features:**
- Play/Pause
- Cue
- Track search buttons
- Tempo fader
- Jog control
- 4 programmable Hot points
- In/Out loop buttons with 1/4, 1/8, 1/16, and 1/32 time intervals
- Master mode
- Sync mode
- Flux mode
- Track position finger changer

Additional available features in Traktor Pro (refer to the guide at http://www.kvasha.us/guide/midi-dj/):
- LCD display showing track name, time (m:s:f), and track position indicator.

**Mixer:**
- Left/Right volume level faders
- Crossfader
- Mic gain fader
- Main output level protected fader (to prevent rapid volume changes)
- Hi, Mid, and Low frequency regulators
- Kill Hi, Mid, and Low buttons
- Gain control
- 3 FX regulators per channel
- 3 FX turn on/off buttons per channel

Additional available features in Traktor Pro (refer to the guide at http://www.kvasha.us/guide/midi-dj/):
- LCD left/right and main output level indicators
- File browsing using Up & Down keys
- Load to Deck A or B buttons
- Phones cueA & cueB buttons

To utilize all the features of Midi DJ remote lite, please consult the user's guide and watch the demonstration videos at http://www.kvasha.us/guide/midi-dj/

Demo video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZfV3kv906lE

Better still, DJ it! showcases precisely how to use these tools effectively as it offers a personalized educational experience to guide new DJs and veteran mixers alike!

Learn to mix. 
Having the perfect tools is one thing, but you need to know how to use them! Thankfully, DJ it! is all about doing just that. Whatever your ability level, DJ it! offers lessons that will help you master critical techniques that are essential for every DJ. 

Quiz
Start by taking a simple questionnaire to let DJ it! analyze your skill level! Study up and attempt more challenging quizzes to earn high scores and expand your knowledge.

Glossary 
Faders, Pitch Sliders, Filters, Channels, Turntables, Decks, Mixers... Don't panic! Our extensive glossary covers every piece of language that every Dj needs.

Dj Tips
Master looping, explore creating hot cues and learn the ins-and-outs of the mashup with quick tips tailored to a variety of skills levels and requirements.

Tutorials 
Here you can learn how to use every single aspect of DJ it! incredible turntable set up. Explore every feature of your mobile mixing desk and tap on whatever you need to learn more about. With tutorials, you'll be mixing like a pro in no time!

Practice makes perfect.
DJ it! also offers an unrivaled mobile mixing set up that makes creating fresh music just as easy as it is to get up and dance to it! However, that doesn’t mean it’s not for experts too! Aside from lessons, it offers a complete Djing package that any advanced Dj could use to scratch, mash, edit, loop and fade their way to the top, all from their pocket!

Your set-up includes: 
- Automatic BPM detection
- Tap to adjust BPM, merely tap the track to sync!
- All the PRO FX you need including Delay, Reverb, Flanger, Gate, High/Low-Pass, Phaser, Bit Crusher, Roll, Reverse.
- Loops: from 1/16 to 64
- Up to 4 Hot Cues per deck!
- Automated audio FX sync on the BPM.
- Three band EQ.
- HD recording with automatic saving and uploading to your library so you'll never lose a mix.
- Support for all major audio formats including MP3, AAC, WAV, AIFF

Welcome to DJ it! - your new one-stop shop for all your mixing needs. 
Study up because it’s time to learn how to mix your masterpiece!
